sub_title: PhD Linguistics, EAP & ESP-Teacher/Course Developer, EFL & NT2 (Dutch) Teacher, Language Specialist, Published Academic Author
summary:
- Versatile, qualified teacher: CELTA (Pass B), PhD in Linguistics.
- Taught EAP, EFL, Dutch as Second Language and at many university courses at universities and language centres in Australia, Asia and Europe.
- EAP/ESP course development.
- Highly experienced with online teaching
- Experience with Kaltura, Brightspace, Moodle and Blackboard online teaching and learning platforms
- Studied and worked in different cultural and linguistic environments
- Well-developed intercultural communication and people skills
- Published academic researcher
